= Arnoldo Martínez Verdugo

*Corriente: los renovadores. Cada consejo suyo fortalece a su corriente — y las otras participan menos.*

First Secretary since 1963. A sign painter from Sinaloa who taught himself four languages and the entire heretical library — Gramsci before it was fashionable, Togliatti when it was dangerous. He runs the Party the way a good doctor runs a ward for the chronically ill: no miracles promised, no patient abandoned. His enemies inside the Party call him cautious. His enemies outside it have thicker files on him than on anyone living.

