on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 6; last_advisor_action = 1; ax_sovietico -= 3; fac_renovadores += 4; moscow_relation -= 2; fac_renovadores += 2; fac_ortodoxos -= 1; fac_nueva_izquierda -= 1

Mimeographed Togliatti, Gramsci in the study circles, a seminar on "the Mexican road" that says nothing censurable and means everything. The ortodoxos smell it — they always smell it — but you cannot expel a man for his bookshelf. Yet.

@verdugo_unidad
title: La unidad de la izquierda
subtitle: The patient work of fusion — the scattered left toward one party, one registro, one address for the future.
card-image: img/portraits/verdugo.jpeg
choose-if: advisor_action_timer == 0
